   <taskbody>
      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Current Budget  Estimate</uicontrol> page provides a consolidated view of all items that are part of approved  budget estimate and all of its approved revisions.<note class="- topic/note ">If the project does not have any approved budget, then the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">CURRENT BUDGET ITEMS</uicontrol> page is blank.</note>
         </p>
      </context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the module menu, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Projects</uicontrol>
            </cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">PROJECTS</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the list page, double-click the required project, and in the navigation pane, expand the project folder.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the navigation pane, expand <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Budget Management</uicontrol>, and then click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Current Budget </uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">CURRENT BUDGET ITEMS</uicontrol> page is displayed.</info>
            <info product="Include_PG_Content" class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <fig product="PG_Screenshot" class="- topic/fig ">
                  <title class="- topic/title ">Current Budget Items Page</title>
                  <image href="../../Icons/Screenshots_Icons/Current_Budget.jpg"
                         class="- topic/image "
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </info>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Total Amount in $</uicontrol> field displays the sum of amounts of all items of the approved budget estimate and all of its revisions. </info>
         </step>
